translation[7]{c,v,t}:
  2,106,"Ngatukufutatu Ȃya jilijose kapena kujiliŵasya, ikaŵeje tukwikanajo jine jambone kupunda jalakwejo kapena jakulandana najo, ana ngankumanyilila kuti Allah pa chindu chilichose aŵele Jwakombola"
  2,107,Ana ngankumanyilila kuti Allah akwete uchimwene wa kumawunde ni petaka? Soni nganinkola jenumanja kaligoselo ata nkulupusyo jwangaŵaga Allah
  2,108,"Kapena nkusaka (Asilamummwe) kuti mum'busyeje Ntenga jwenuﷺmpela yaŵatiji pakuwusyidwa Musa kalakala (iwusyo yachalu)? Soni jwachasagule ukafili pakusumanya ni chikulupi, nikuti amasile mwasokonechele kuleka litala lyagoloka"
  2,109,"Ŵajinji mwa achinsyene itabu (Ayuda ni Akilisito) aŵele ali nkusachilila yanti ali am'buchisye (Asilamummwe) ku ukafili panyuma pakulupilila kwenu, ligongo lya litima lyakutyochela kwa ŵanganyao achimisyene, panyuma pakuonechela kwa jamanjao chakuona (jwali Muhammadi ﷺ), basi mwakululuchilani nikwaleka mpaka Allah ayichenalyo lilamusi Lyakwe, chisimu Allah pa chindu chilichose aŵele Jwakombola"
  2,110,"Soni jimikani Swala mwakolosya ni ntoleje Zaka, soni mu chambone chilichose chinkulilongochesya chinkachisimane kwa Allah, chisimu Allah ichindu yankutenda aŵele Jwakuilolechesya"
  2,111,"Soni ŵatite: “Ngaŵa nkuja kwinjila ku Mbepo ni ikaŵeje jwali Myuda kapena Nkilisito.” Yele ni isako yao. Jilani: “Ikani nao umboni wenu naga nkuŵecheta yakuona.”"
  2,112,"(Ngwamba!) Nambo kuti mundu jwachajipeleche ngope jakwe kwa Allah (pakunda Usilamu), ni ali jwakolosya (pa Usilamu wakwe), jwele nijuchakapate malipilo gakwe kwa M'mbujegwe, soni ngasaja kuŵa nioga, ngasaja kuŵa soni ŵakudandaula"